=head1 INITIALIZATION

=begin html
<PRE>
<UL>
<LI><B><FONT SIZE="+1">In the case of Real Home Link</FONT></B>
</UL>
                    
      LFN0    NUT0     HA0    NODE0     R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <---- |       |       |       |       | 1.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |     NUTX      |       |       |       |       |
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <-------------------- |       |       | 2.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       |       |       | 3.Neighbor Solicitation (NUD)
        |       |       |       |       |       |       | 4.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       |       |       | 5.Binding Update
        |       | <---- |       |       |       |       | 6.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
                    
        1. Send Router Advertisement. (HA0 -> HA0_allnode_multi)
        2. Send Router Advertisement. (R1 -> R1_allnode_multi)
        3. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (NUD). (NUT0 -> HA0)
        4. (no reply)
        5. Receive Binding Update to HA0. (NUTX -> HA0)
            # The Mobile Router Flag (R) is set to 1.
        6. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUTX)
            # The Mobile Router Flag (R) is set to 1.
                    
</PRE>

=end html

=head1 TEST PROCEDURE

=begin html
<PRE>
                    
      LFN0    NUTX     HA0    NODE0     R1      R2     CN0
        |     NUT0      |       |       |       |       | 
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <---- |       |       |       |       | 1.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | --------------------> |       |       | 2.Neighbor Solicitation (NUD)
        |       |       |       |       |       |       | 3.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       |       |       | 4.Binding Update
        |       | <---- |       |       |       |       | 5.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       |       |       | 6.Neighbor Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <------------ |       |       |       | 7.Router Solicitation
        |       | ------------> |       |       |       | 8.Router Advertisement (*1)
        |       |       |       |       |       |       |
                    
        1. Send Router Advertisement. (HA0 -> HA0_allnode_multi)
        2. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (NUD). (NUTX -> R1)
        3. (no reply)
            # Wait during a maximum of 3 seconds(RFC2461).
        4. Receive Binding Update. (NUT0 -> HA0)
            # The Lifetime field is set to 0.
            # The Mobile Router Flag (R) is set to 1.
        5. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUT0)
            # The Mobile Router Flag (R) is set to 1.
        6. Send Neighbor Acknowledgement. (NUT0 -> NUT0_allnode_multi)
        7. Send Router Solicitation. (NODE0 -> NUT0)
        8. Receive Router Advertisement. (NUT0 -> NODE0)
                    
    Focus Packet Format:
        7. Router Solicitation Data is:
            IPv6 header
                source          = global address of node0
                destination     = egress global address of nut0
            ICMPv6 header
              Router Solicitation
              Source link-layer address option
                link-layer address = node0
                    
        8. Router Advertisement Data is:
            IPv6 header
                source          = egress link-local address of nut0
                destination     = global address of node0 or
                                = all node multicast
            ICMPv6 header
              Router Advertisement
                Lifetime        = 0
</PRE>

=end html

=head1 JUDGEMENT

=begin html
<PRE>
 (*1) PASS: NODE0 receives Router Advertisement from Mobile Router.
            Then, check whether this packet fills all of the following,
             - The Router Lifetime field is set to 0.
</PRE>

=end html

